Interface HasMu

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CylindricalBarMagnet, CylindricalMagnet, LineMagneticDipole, MagneticDipole

    public interface HasMu
    WorldObjects that have a Mu should implement HasMu Implementing this interface allows read / write access to your Mu property.
